member.name: P:BodyComp.My.Resources.Resources.resfiReleaseNotes
member.summary:
Looks up a localized string similar to Body Composition Calculator Release Notes:
Note: Special markings key is located at bottom of release notes.
Version 1.5.6.3 - INITIAL RELEASE
Fixes:
Bugs:
Special Markings: An asterisk (*) before a bug signifies that it was found after the release notes were finalized for that build. A double asterisk (**) before a bug or fix signifies a feature that broke due to website maintenance. An asterisk and a capital P (*P) before a bug signifies a postponed bug. An asteris [rest of string was truncated]";.
